## Stage F — Historical + Backtesting

After strategies.

Flow:

```text
historical data
↓

strategy

↓

simulated trades

↓

PnL report
```

Package:

```text
backtesting
```

Now you can answer:

> Would my strategy have worked last year?

Very strong project feature.

